http://developer.wordnik.com/

The Wordnik API lets you request 
	1. definitions, 
	2. example sentences, 
	3. spelling suggestions, 
	4. related words like synonyms and antonyms, 
	5. phrases containing a given word, 
	6. word autocompletion, 
	7. random words, 
	8. words of the day, 
	and much more.

Sign up for a developer key at
http://developer.wordnik.com/